room_title: Escape room "The Principal's Office" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We had a blast in the Principal’s office today! We barely escaped! Great for families.

room_title: Escape room "The Principal's Office" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: So much fun! The staff was very friendly!! Thank you Shannon for your help:) The boys loved escaping the Principal's office!

room_title: Escape room "The Principal's Office" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We did the “Principal’s Office” with six 7th grade boys. So much fun! They loved it and finished with 9:41 minutes left. Looking forward to trying harder rooms in the future.

room_title: Escape room "The Principal's Office" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We went with our family (kids too) and did the Principal's office. We had a blast! Great staff and a fun challenge. We will be going back to do the other rooms soon!

room_title: Escape room "The Principal's Office" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: This was an outstanding experience for my daughter's 13th birthday. We brought the whole family (younger sisters included) and all enjoyed the Principal's Office. Jordan was an incredible game master and so helpful to us throughout the experience. We will for sure be back to play!
